imdb.title: The Return of Hwang Geum-Bok
plot: A mother dedicates her life to the betterment of her daughter. Nevertheless, the daughter is ashamed of her poor mother. After her mother disappears, the daughter comes to terms with the magnitude of her mother's sacrifice.
